{"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"typedef","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:BFv(#*$objc(cs)NSString#*$objc(cs)NSError)","text":"void (^)(NSString *, NSError *)"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"PushwooshRegistrationHandler"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"Overview","level":2,"text":"Overview"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This closure is called when the device registration process finishes, either successfully or with an error."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The handler receives two parameters:","type":"text"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"token","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": The push token string if registration succeeded, or "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":" if it failed"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"error","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": An error object if registration failed, or "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":" if it succeeded"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"level":2,"anchor":"Example","text":"Example","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Handle registration result with UI updates and backend sync:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["func registerForNotifications() {","    let registrationHandler: PushwooshRegistrationHandler = { token, error in","        if let error = error {","            self.logger.error(\"Push registration failed: \\(error.localizedDescription)\")","            self.updateNotificationStatus(.failed)","            return","        }","","        guard let token = token else { return }","","        self.logger.info(\"Push token received: \\(token.prefix(20))...\")","        self.updateNotificationStatus(.registered)","","        self.syncPushTokenWithBackend(token)","    }","","    Pushwoosh.configure.registerForPushNotifications(withCompletion: registrationHandler)","}","","func syncPushTokenWithBackend(_ token: String) {","    let hwid = Pushwoosh.configure.getHWID()","    apiClient.post(\"\/devices\/register\", body: [","        \"push_token\": token,","        \"hwid\": hwid,","        \"platform\": \"ios\"","    ])","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"}],"kind":"content"}],"sections":[],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshframework\/pushwooshregistrationhandler"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"seeAlsoSections":[{"title":"Related Documentation","identifiers":["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS\/documentation\/PushwooshFramework\/PushwooshErrorHandler"]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS\/documentation\/PushwooshFramework\/PushwooshRegistrationHandler"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Completion handler called when push notification registration completes."}],"metadata":{"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"PushwooshRegistrationHandler","kind":"identifier"}],"fragments":[{"text":"PushwooshRegistrationHandler","kind":"identifier"}],"symbolKind":"typealias","roleHeading":"Type Alias","role":"symbol","title":"PushwooshRegistrationHandler","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshFramework"}],"externalID":"c:PWTypes.h@T@PushwooshRegistrationHandler"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS\/documentation\/PushwooshFramework"]]},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS/documentation/PushwooshFramework":{"type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Push notification SDK for iOS applications.","type":"text"}],"title":"PushwooshFramework","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshframework","role":"collection","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS\/documentation\/PushwooshFramework"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS/documentation/PushwooshFramework/PushwooshRegistrationHandler":{"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS\/documentation\/PushwooshFramework\/PushwooshRegistrationHandler","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshframework\/pushwooshregistrationhandler","fragments":[{"text":"PushwooshRegistrationHandler","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"PushwooshRegistrationHandler","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Completion handler called when push notification registration completes.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS/documentation/PushwooshFramework/PushwooshErrorHandler":{"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Completion handler called when an operation fails."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS\/documentation\/PushwooshFramework\/PushwooshErrorHandler","title":"PushwooshErrorHandler","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshframework\/pushwoosherrorhandler","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"PushwooshErrorHandler","kind":"identifier"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"typealias"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"PushwooshErrorHandler","kind":"identifier"}]}},"variantOverrides":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"patch":[{"value":"PushwooshErrorHandler","op":"replace","path":"\/references\/doc:~1~1com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS~1documentation~1PushwooshFramework~1PushwooshErrorHandler\/title"},{"value":[{"text":"PushwooshErrorHandler","kind":"identifier"}],"path":"\/references\/doc:~1~1com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS~1documentation~1PushwooshFramework~1PushwooshErrorHandler\/fragments","op":"replace"}]}]}